funcs.doc:
Escape returns s with the HTML-significant characters &, <, >, ", and '
replaced by their entity equivalents:

	& -> &amp;
	< -> &lt;
	> -> &gt;
	" -> &quot;
	' -> &#39;

If s contains none of these characters, it is returned unchanged.

